snippet.title: Liana K
snippet.description:
Home of Lady Bits and BOSSFIGHT! Looking to improve the dialogue around video games and reduce stigma against gamers.

It's not all game content.  It's other stuff gamers are interested in too! There's a focus on gaming culture on this channel. If you're looking for more gameplay, check out my Twitch channel, Tuesdays at 6pm Eastern and Thursdays at 1pm Eastern! https://www.twitch.tv/redlianak

For media requests please contact Vajira Ranaviraja @ vajira@krt-associates.com

For all other inquiries, consider twitter.  @redlianak
